snippet.title: Toon Wars Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Exciting online tank battles.

Tank battle players from around the world!

Cartoonish real-time tank battles! 
An exciting game with a lot of interesting maps and a possibility to customize your tank. 

Improve your tank and drive it right into the battle to crush enemies! 

You can choose any game mode: team or free-for-all. And all of this comes for FREE! 

Play as much as you can to gain experience and create your own clan for more fun!

Upgrade your tank
Complete daily quests and earn game currency
Join your friends, create your clan
Be the first on the weekly top players list (region/country/world)
Have fun! This is what we created the game for!

Download Links:

Google Play - https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.extremedevelopers.toonboom
iOS - https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/toon-wars-3d/id1016351204
Windows 8 и 10 - https://www.microsoft.com/store/apps/9NBLGGH1Z1WG

Community pages:
FB - https://www.facebook.com/ToonWars/
BK - https://vk.com/toonwarsgame
OK - http://ok.ru/game/toonwars
MM - https://my.mail.ru/apps/736174
